> Clone into a directory of your wish
> cd into cloned dir & run 'ruby install.rb'
> Open mvim and run :BundleInstall

It will take few mins based on the network speed to install all the plugins specified in vimrc

> Install Inconsolata-for-powerline font from http://favstar.fm/users/nicksergeant/status/157562479759736833
> Install exuberant ctags. The ctag that comes with mac does not have needed options.
  >> sudo mv /usr/bin/ctags{,.old}
  >> brew install ctags-exuberant

Close and open mvim. Things should be fine.
